title: We Talking Business Like It's 1999, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO56
description: If he could travel back through time to 1999 (in a Lambo, not a DeLorean), what advice would millionaire entrepreneur Andy Frisella give to his younger, inexperienced self? It's the same advice he'd give anyone on ground zero of building their empire.
